data.description:
Seller now offering 5k to use as buyer chooses, towards closing costs or solar panels! Conveniently located, South side, Brick home on corner lot with side entry garage. This one checks all the boxes! Spacious living area with wood burning fireplace, vaulted ceilings, and stained concrete flooring. Recently installed flooring in bedrooms. NO CARPET. Most of the interior has a fresh coat of paint. Kitchen has stainless appliances, Granite counter tops, pantry, fridge will stay.  Both bathrooms have been updated with tiled showers. Primary bedroom is light and bright, with vaulted ceilings and double closets, for a roomy feel and great storage. Backyard is fenced and has a nice covered patio.
Panel Box has been updated. Water heater 2023. Wylie East Schools.
